{"tid":37132,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【三點九沈大師】大師：暫時唔好咁進取住 2016-12-13","createTime":"2016-12-13T07:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T02:34:00.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d76283a35c4eb6c75613f6684839e24fed1fb301","tid":37132,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"【三點九沈大師】大師：暫時唔好咁進取住<br />\n2016-12-13 15:10:49 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【三點九沈大師】大師：暫時唔好咁進取住<br />\n<br />\n又到《三點九沈大師》時間，今朝反反覆覆，曾經抽升跟住又倒跌，個市最低去到22930點，穿22300之後又反彈，其實睇到港股冇乜力，就算A股已經有個反彈勢頭似乎港股都抽唔起。<br />\n<br />\n今日o黎計我覺得就唔好太過進取喇，仍然靠邊站啦，走咗貨嘅算喇，沽住嘅，睇情況決定食唔食糊定係靠邊站，我覺得點都留少少淡倉睇多日，睇聽日情況再試底之後先至考慮入場博反彈，暫時唔好咁進取住。"},{"pid":"4bcf64892b4cfa8acfe35da10f27440fd8b602a3","tid":37132,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:15:10.000Z","msg":"二師兄，睇路，小心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2d45d5a9009ca31fabb65a70c36d18c37d1abc","tid":37132,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:15:24.000Z","msg":"啫係要進取啲？"},{"pid":"ad75f5cd55db930824091cc4baa834eea276fe1b","tid":37132,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:16:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ALL IN！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"bb046eb187525f1a418a582da6b8cbafe8c2453f","tid":37132,"uid":13308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:19:19.000Z","msg":"等睇倒升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df885e4b9f72b1de43d83487b348e357dd6bb54","tid":37132,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b275e631cf21fdbfddb2c0db6d16b9909856498","tid":37132,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:31:53.000Z","msg":"大師明燈指路，即allin，不經不覺全倉鳥。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /